ght: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">With Creator Payouts, it&#8217;s both. Roug=
hly 15 million views at $0.0002 per view, paid directly into my account.&#1=
60;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26=
px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">That combination &#8211; legibility and liquidity =
&#8211; is as alluring as it is dangerous. It can tempt you into short-term=
 moves at the expense of long-term ones.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64=
, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>I=
n </span><em><a href=3D"https://link.sbstck.com/redirect/7c54993a-f09e-4c33=
-b45b-c35ce3f3cff9?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-=
6m8ExkRNpU" rel style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); text-decoration: underline=
;">The Great Online Game</a></em><span>, I wrote that, &#8220;Medium-level =
Twitter is Threads and engagement hacks. Twitter Mastery is indistinguishab=
