-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">You do so at the risk =
of getting stuck on medium, polishing away exactly the unique and weird cur=
iosities and obsessions that might attract the other people with the same w=
eird curiosities and obsessions. And you do so at the risk of being labeled=
, subconsciously, as an engagement hacker by the very people whose engageme=
nt might matter most to you.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); f=
ont-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>As markets ge=
t more liquid and legible, it&#8217;s too easy to be mid, to be the rat in =
