aa-1046-4e46-93b6-cb4fb56ae6b2?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjml=
XXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); text-decoratio=
n: underline;">market for </a><em><a href=3D"https://link.sbstck.com/redire=
ct/967340aa-1046-4e46-93b6-cb4fb56ae6b2?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_Z=
lNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); text-=
decoration: underline;">intelligence</a></em><span> is even becoming more l=
iquid and legible.&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font=
-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Nine times out of ten,=
 the right move is to simply and gratefully take advantage of that legibili=
ty and liquidity. Buy a SpaceX rideshare instead of building your own rocke=
t. Use AWS instead of racking your own servers. Plug in OpenAI&#8217;s API =
instead of building your own foundation model. Hell, go farm views on Twitt=
er to make the money to do that thing you really want to do, that only you =
can do.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-=
height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">If the liquid and legible market is in s=
omething that&#8217;s not core to who you are or what you want to do, by al=
l means, squeeze that liquidity and legibility for all they&#8217;re worth.=
 If paying someone $9.76 to pick up donuts means I get to spend 30 minutes =
writing or playing with my kids, I&#8217;ll make that trade all day. If Twi=
tter wants to pay me to do exactly what I&#8217;d do anyway, awesome.&#160;=
</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px;=
 margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>Just beware of the temptation to take the liqui=
d and legible path </span><em>ten</em><span> times out of ten.&#160;</span>=
</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px;=
 margin: 0 0 20px 0;">As markets become more liquid and legible, beta impro=
ves while alpha erodes. The average person in those markets is better off, =
but it&#8217;s harder to outperform. It&#8217;s easier than ever to make $1=
,000 by tweeting threads, and harder than ever to stand out as unique by do=
ing so.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-=
height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>Know what you want to stand out fo=
r, how you&#8217;re </span><a href=3D"https://link.sbstck.com/redirect/67a7=
7d59-3b6f-41ff-9a27-4de38f933466?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZj=
mlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); text-decorat=
ion: underline;">different</a><span>, what you can do that no one else can =
that can&#8217;t be captured by an algorithm or simple market signals, at l=
east not yet.&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size=
: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>There&#8217;s a marke=
t for </span><em>almost</em><span> everything.&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"=
color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20p=
